你能够调用以下的API:
[['MarketDataCollector.collect_macro_data', {'name': 'MarketDataCollector.collect_macro_data', 'description': 'This function collects macroeconomic data for specified countries.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'countries', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of country names for which macroeconomic data is required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'macro_data', 'description': 'A list of macroeconomic data for each country.'}]}], ['ExchangeRuleFetcher.get_exchange_rules', {'name': 'ExchangeRuleFetcher.get_exchange_rules', 'description': 'This function fetches trading rules for the main stock exchanges in a specified country.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'country', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The country for which exchange rules are required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'exchange_rules', 'description': 'Trading rules for the main stock exchange in the specified country.'}]}], ['FundPerformanceAnalyzer.find_quant_funds', {'name': 'FundPerformanceAnalyzer.find_quant_funds', 'description': 'This function finds quant funds with successful experience in a specified market type.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'number_of_funds', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of funds to find.'}, {'name': 'market_type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of market, e.g., emerging, developed.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'funds', 'description': 'A list of quant funds with details including performance and strategy.'}]}], ['PolicyImpactEvaluator.analyze_financial_policy', {'name': 'PolicyImpactEvaluator.analyze_financial_policy', 'description': 'This function analyzes the impact of recent financial policies on quant investments in specified countries.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'countries', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of country names for which policy impact analysis is required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'impact_analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of how recent financial policies have affected quant investments in each country.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `MarketDataCollector.collect_macro_data` 并传入 `countries`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "MarketDataCollector.collect_macro_data",
    "args": "{'countries': ['Brazil', 'India', 'South Africa']}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
